sellerCard.oneLiner: Dedicated bubble io developer for bubble web and mobile apps
sellerCard.description:
I am Devraj, an experienced Bubble Developer with experience of 7+ years in the web development field. I have 4+ years of bubble and other no code tools development experience. I am here to help you bring your MVP idea to life within 14 days only!

What I promise to deliver Best!
1. Creating Complex Data Structures
2. Creating Data Logics and Data Flow
3. Third-party integrations via API
4. Payment gateways Integrations
5. Adding Triggered Conditions and Authentications
6. Optimization/ Responsiveness of Design
7. Multiuser Logins/ Dashboards
8. Creating Basic Design flow

description.content:
Do you need a quick prototype to test your idea? Or are you ready to create a full service or marketplace?


Bubble.io is the fastest way to transform the concept into a fully functioning product in just a few days. It's a great CMS for creating simple sites as well as complex applications like Airbnb, Uber, eBay, etc.


What you can order:

  • Responsive design
  • Message and notification system
  • API integrations, custom plugins, and custom code elements for Bubble applications;
  • UX/UI design development and implementation;
  • Payment gateways
  • Social Logins
  • Geo-location


Bubble is the way to go if you're an entrepreneur with a great business idea who wants to ship it as soon as possible.


You will receive a completely customized web and mobile application for your startup idea, which you can test in the market, get feedback on, and use to present to investors.


You will need to provide mockups or wireframes, a detailed description of the app, and examples of similar projects.


Contact me and let's discuss your next idea


Before Placing order let's chat and understand your requirements before hand!
